:: The Lossy Everyday
<div class="lcontainer">
	<h2><center>And then a pause â‡¢ The Lossy Everyday</center></h2>
    <img class ="lcover" src="https://i0.wp.com/blackhaunts.mp285.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/cropped-KoS.jpg" height="300" width="100%">
