<div class="lcontainer">
<h2><center>Common sympathy â‡¢ for the children</center></h2>
<img class ="lcover" src="https://i0.wp.com/blackhaunts.mp285.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/sheep2.png" height="300" width="100%">
